data.description: *** Assumable VA loan at 2.5% fixed rate, certain conditions apply. Inquire with listing agent***     This STUNNING home is a must see! One of the best floor plans!  Large gourmet kitchen that opens to the spacious family room, kitchen has a huge center island, an abundance of cabinets, gorgeous quartz countertops, upgraded stainless steel appliances, farmhouse sink, LARGE walk in pantry and upgraded pendant lighting. The formal dining area is massive and will accommodate a LARGE dining room table, family room is cozy and has beautiful views of the backyard. The large primary suite is secluded from the rest of the bedrooms and is very spacious with a sliding door to the backyard. The primary bathroom has been upgraded to a step in stone shower with stone tiling around the soaking tub as well. The closet is HUGE and was definitely a selling point for my client when they originally purchased the home. LOTS of storage! The 3 secondary bedrooms are all spacious in size with large closets. This gorgeous home does NOT lack storage, there are 2 additional linen closets in the hallway as well. The secondary bathroom has solid surface countertops and a tub/shower combo.  The laundry room is massive in size with plenty of room to add storage cabinets/ folding table etc. It's plumbed for a utility sink as well. The backyard is private with no rear neighbors peering into your backyard! Large California room patio, yard was professionally landscaped with low maintenance turf, concrete patio, and lush plants.  Don't let the pictures fool you, the home has a 3 car tandem garage!    Don't miss out on this one!
